# The Open-RAG-Bench-derived dataset is generated locally and never committed:
#   * it is CC BY-NC 4.0 (non-commercial) — this repo is Apache-2.0
#     (see README.md, "Licensing"); vendoring NC data would taint the tree
#   * it is large (≈1000 full arXiv papers) and fully reproducible from
#     generate.py
#
# Keep this folder's README and this .gitignore tracked; ignore everything else
# (corpus/, qa.jsonl, config.json, run.py, generate.py, ATTRIBUTION.md, caches).
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
